      GREATEST(-60, LEAST(delay, 180))::FLOAT AS delay,
      LEAST(distance, 3000)::FLOAT AS distance,
      time
    FROM 'http://localhost:5173/data/flights.parquet'
DESCRIBE SELECT "delay" AS "col0", "time" AS "col1", "distance" AS "col2" FROM "flights" AS "source"
DESCRIBE SELECT COUNT(*)::INTEGER AS "column" FROM "flights" AS "source" GROUP BY ALL
